<p>Lifestyle blogger Connie Cao, from Melbourne, has shared some of her beginner's tips after baking her own loaves of sourdough bread every week.</p>

<p>After lots of trial and error, Connie said she discovered the best tool to score the dough to perfection.</p>

<p>'I used to use a knife but it was way too blunt. Then I discovered the razor blade and oh my goodness. What a game changer,' she wrote on her blog.</p>

